WEBVTT

00:00:00.780 --> 00:00:02.779
I've got this grudge

00:00:03.779 --> 00:00:09.539
I'm holding it in but it's so heavy

00:00:09.539 --> 00:00:11.539
It pulls me down

00:00:11.539 --> 00:00:17.079
Wish I could turn this around

00:00:17.079 --> 00:00:24.140
I understand each

00:00:24.140 --> 00:00:25.140
To forgive

00:00:25.140 --> 00:00:28.620
But it's not easy

00:00:28.620 --> 00:00:33.079
If it's not these thoughts

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:36.079
Bring forgiveness to a whole
